fr.univrennes1.cri.jtacl.core.monitor
Class ProbePosition

java.lang.Object
  fr.univrennes1.cri.jtacl.core.monitor.ProbePosition

public class ProbePosition
extends java.lang.Object

Describes the position of a probe.
The position is defined by the IfaceLink link of the incoming interface (incoming), the IfaceLink link of the outgoing interface (outgoing) of the probe and the IPNet IP address of the nexthop.
The two IfaceLink must refered to the same NetworkEquipment equipment and must be set in the order: 'incoming, outgoing, nexthop'.

Author:
Patrick Lamaiziere
